<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>د ن أ<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c4">[١٨٥٧ - د ن أ]</span><a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>دنُؤَ يَدنُؤ، دَناءَةً ودُنُوءًا ودُنُوءةً، فهو دَنِيء<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c5">• دنُؤ الشَّخصُ:</span> دنَأ، لَؤُمَ فِعْلُه وخَبُث، صار دنيئًا <span class="c1">"رَجُل دَنِيء: خسيسٌ دُون"</span>.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>